#include <bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
typedef long long LL;
const int MAXN = 100000 + 10;

LL val[MAXN], cnt[MAXN], L;
int id[MAXN], n;

bool cmp(int a, int b) {return val[a] < val[b];}

void sol() {
  scanf("%d%lld", &n, &L);
  LL tot(0);
  for (int i = 0; i < n; ++ i) {
    scanf("%lld", val + i);
    id[i] = i; tot += val[i];
  }
  sort(id, id + n, cmp);
  id[n] = n; val[n] = L + 1;
  if (val[id[n - 1]] > L || tot > L) {puts("-1"); return;}
  tot = 0;
  for (int i = 0; i < n; ++ i) {
    int x = id[i];
    if (tot != val[x] - 1) {puts("-1"); return;}
    cnt[x] = (val[id[i + 1]] - 1) / val[x];
    tot += cnt[x] * val[x];
  }
  if (tot != L) {puts("-1"); return;}
  for (int i = 0; i < n; ++ i) printf("%lld ", cnt[i]); puts("");
}

int main() {
  int T; scanf("%d", &T);
  for (int _ = 0; _ < T; ++_) {
    sol();
  }
  return 0;
}
